lead_paragraph: Wayne Rooney may not start Manchester United's Europa League match against Ukrainian side Zorya Luhansk for his own protection as he is struggling with a back injury, manager Jose Mourinho said on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Injured Rooney May Not Start Against Zorya, Says Mourinho
headline.main: Injured Rooney May Not Start Against Zorya, Says Mourinho
